snippet.title: HOMERUN CLASH, Season 3 Update!!
snippet.description:
"Hit the Ball Out of the Park!
Real-time Global Home Run Battle!
Become the World's Best Home Run Hitter! "

※Compete with Home Run Hitters From All Over the World!! ※
A total of 10,320,342,720 home runs have been hit in Homerun Clash!  
Over 10 billion home runs! How far can we go?
